    "Research in Parameter-efficient Transfer Learning (Houlsby et al., 2019) such as Adapters (Hu et al., 2021; Dettmers et al., 2024) and Prefixtuning (Li and Liang, 2021) have significantly lower the barrier of fine-tuning LLMs/VLMs under resource-constrained scenarios (Cai et al., 2024)."
